 "Seasons of Wither"
 "I Wanna Know Why"
 "Walkin' The Dog"
 "Walk This Way"
 "Lick and a Promise"
 "Get The Lead Out"
 "Draw the Line"
 "Sweet Emotion"
 "Same Old Song and Dance"
 "Milk Cow Blues"
 "Toys in the Attic"

Miembros de la banda
